@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vdfmef(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((0.28 - (v0 + 0.86 * v1 + 0.06)) + (tmp * v2))
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.exp((v2 + 0.39 + v1 + 0.81)))
    v1 = (((v2 + 0.88 + tmp + 0.86) * tmp) / 0.74)
    v2 = (v1 - 0.20)
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.abs((tmp + 0.79 - v2 + 0.88)))
    data[tid] = v0
